sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Subject
    participant R as Relay
    participant A as Attestor
    participant V as Verifier

    S->>R: publish assertion event (any kind)
    Note over R: event ID = abc123

    A->>R: fetch assertion event
    R-->>A: returns claim

    A->>R: publish kind 31000<br/>["e","abc123","relay","assertion"]

    V->>R: {"kinds":[31000],"#e":["abc123"]}
    R-->>V: attestation event(s)

    V->>R: verify assertion event exists<br/>and authored by subject
    V->>V: weight attestors by WoT
